byline.contributor: Rami Nazzal contributed reporting from Ramallah, West Bank.

lead_paragraph: Graphic footage emerged of Israeli soldiers roughly carrying a young Palestinian man they had shot during a clash in the West Bank.

headline.main: Video of Fatally Wounded Teenager Sparks Palestinian Rage
